<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="Pterocles_orientalis#Verhalten"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">Verhalten</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="Pterocles_orientalis#Fortpflanzung"><span class="tocnumber">4</span> <span class="toctext">Fortpflanzung</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-5"><a href="Pterocles_orientalis#Bestand"><span class="tocnumber">5</span> <span class="toctext">Bestand</span></a></li>
